{# Human-readable heading for a namespace.

   The `namespace_mapping` text map wins when it has an entry for the namespace;
   it exists for titles that casing alone cannot produce (`cicd` -> `CI/CD`).
   Otherwise the id is title-cased with known initialisms upper-cased
   (`http` -> `HTTP`). Both are configured in your `.weaver.toml`. #}

{% macro namespace(ns) -%}
{%- set mapped = ns | map_text("namespace_mapping", "") -%}
{{ mapped if mapped else ns | title_case | acronym }}
{%- endmacro %}
